<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <% include partials/head/home-head %>
  <body>
    <% include partials/nav %>
    <link href="/styles/home.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
    
    <div class="header-image">
      <div id="homeLoginSection">
      <% include partials/login-links %>
       <p id="homeWelcome" class="pull-right text-muted snall"><%= message %><span id="n"><%= n %></span><span id="u" style="display:none"><%= u %></span></p>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-8">
        <div id="gtLeaderboard" class="leaderboardContainer">
              <h5 class="text-center">GuitarThinker Leaderboard</h5>
              <% if (Parse.User.current()) { %>
              <div id="gtLeaderboardBtnRow" class="leaderboardBtnRow"><span>Sort by: </span><div id="gtLbTopScorersBtn" class="btn btn-sm btn-default">Top Scorers</div><div id="gtLbNearMeBtn" class="btn btn-sm btn-default">Near Me</div></div><% } %>  
        <table class="table">  
        <thead>  
          <tr>  
            <th>#</th>  
            <th>Name</th>  
            <th><a href="/spell-that-chord"><img src="/images/stc/AppIcon40x40.png" alt="Spell That Chord Icon"></a></th>  
            <th>Music<br>Theory<br>Master</th>
            <th>Overall<br>Points</th>
          </tr>  
        </thead>  
        <tbody id="masterLeaderboardTable">  
            
        </tbody>
        </table>

          </div><!--/#gtLeaderboard-->
      </div><!--/.col-->
      <div class="col-md-4"></div><!-- SPACER COLUMN -->
      <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4">
        <h4 style="padding-right: 20px;"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-arrow-left"></span> <span id="homeHeroText"></span></h4>
      </div><!--/.col-->
    </div><!--/.row-->
    </div><!--/.header-image-->
    
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
		<div class="col-sm-4">
			<h2 class="text-center">Games</h2>
            <div class="row">
            <div class="col-sm-6 text-center">
              <div class="homeGameTop">
                <a href="/spell-that-chord"><img src="/images/stc/AppIcon76x76@2x.png" alt="Spell That Chord Large Icon" style="width: 100px; margin: 0 auto;"></a>
              </div>
              <div class="homeGameBottom">
                <small>Practice building chords. Compete against the world!</small>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-6">
              <div class="homeGameTop">
                <a href="music-theory-master">Music Theory Master</a>
              </div>
              <div class="homeGameBottom">
                <small>Music Theory made fun.  A fast paced quiz with study guide (study guide coming soon).</small>
              </div>
            </div>
            </div><!--/row-->
            
		</div>
		<div class="col-sm-4">
			<h2 class="text-center">Apps</h2>
		</div>
		<div class="col-sm-4">
			<h4>This site is dedicated to making learning music easier and more fun.</h4>
			<p></span> Here are some things that are coming very soon:</p>
            <p><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-ok"></span> More games and apps to help you be awesome.</p>
            <p><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-ok"></span> Live leaderboards for each game.</p>
            <p><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-ok"></span> A master GuitarThinker leaderboard that tracks points scored for all games.</p>
            <p><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-ok"></span> Even more awesome stuff.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
        
      <div class="textured-background">
        <h4>Here's what I think:</h4>
        <p>There is a serious lack of cool web 3.0 tools for musicians.  What does that mean?  Stuff like live data, interactivity, mobile device compatibility, and great looking design.  Why?  Well, probably because music education is not a super lucrative market, or maybe just because most musicians are not also programmers.</p>
        <h4>GuitarThinker to the rescue!</h4>
        <p>This site will be a fun place to visit, learn, come back and see what's new.  GuitarThinker will be a place to compete with yourself and others, because competetion motivates us.  This site will have lots of games that are fun to play and teach you music.</p>
        </div><!--/.textured-background-->
    </div><!-- end container -->
    <% include partials/footer %>
    <script src="/js/home.js"></script>  <!-- home js -->
  </body>
</html>
